name: Reponse-pda
article: Reponse. A QnA blockchain service which provides direct compensation and copyright protection for the person that asks the question and for the person that answers the question. Reponse is a service utilized to ask and answer questions. We encourage everyone to utilize the 'question' space for asking and the 'answer' space for answering. It's as simple as that. Ask questions and receive points. Answer questions and receive points. The points earned can be exchanged for Reponse crypto currency. All questions and answers will utilize blockchain technology deeming the content copyright and therefore cannot be changed.
